    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Great Value Alert \u2014 A Genuinely Good Car at a Fair Price! \ud83d\ude97\n\nHere's a vehicle you can feel confident about! This car is in good condition \u2014 it drives well, has been maintained, and is ready to be your reliable everyday companion. You'll notice some normal signs of regular use (think minor cosmetic wear here and there), but mechanically it's in solid shape and performs the way you'd want it to.\n\nNo smoke and mirrors here \u2014 just a dependable, good-condition vehicle priced honestly to move. Whether you're commuting, road-tripping, or just need something you can count on, this one checks the boxes without the premium price of a mint-condition ride.\n\n\u2705 Good mechanical condition\n\u2705 Reliable daily driver\n\u2705 Honestly priced for its tier\n\nCome take a look \u2014 we think you'll agree this one is worth every dollar! \ud83d\udcaa",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront with all potential buyers about its current state. The exterior shows significant wear throughout \u2014 expect multiple scratches, scuffs, dents, and faded or peeling paint in several areas. The body panels show clear signs of age and neglect, and there may be surface rust visible in spots. The interior is similarly worn, with frayed or torn upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and general grime that reflects heavy use over the years. Mechanically, the vehicle runs but has known issues that will require attention \u2014 buyers should anticipate repair costs and should factor that into their decision. This car is best suited for someone comfortable with a project vehicle or who needs basic transportation and has the means to address its shortcomings. We recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're taking on. Priced accordingly to reflect its condition honestly.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in good condition. It runs and drives well with no significant mechanical issues. The exterior shows minor wear consistent with normal use, including some light scratches, but no major damage. The interior is clean and functional with normal signs of use.",
      "price": 33500.0,
